metadata.title: Eagle Nest Sites  - CNF

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  Eagle nest site points with combination of QTM, ITM and nest number. Scale is 1:63,360. Coverages were originally created in 1990 based on 1989 field surveys and USFWS records. They include both active and inactive sites.
